uschrist.org/study/ensign/2006/07/some-must-push-and-some-must-pull?lang=eng\n }}\n* {{cite book\n | last=Jones\n | first=Daniel W.\n | authorlink=Daniel Webster Jones (Mormon)\n | title=[[Forty Years Among the Indians: A True Yet Thrilling Narrative of the Author's Experiences Among the Natives]]\n | year=1890\n | publisher=[[Juvenile Instructor Office]]\n | location=Salt Lake City, Utah\n }}\n* {{cite book\n | last=Hafen\n | first=LeRoy R.\n | authorlink=LeRoy R. Hafen\n | author2=Ann W. Hafen\n | title=Handcarts to Zion: the story of a unique western migration, 1856\u20131860: with contemporary journals, accounts, reports and rosters of members of the ten handcart companies\n | origyear=1960\n | year=1981\n | publisher=Arthur H. Clark Company\n | isbn=0-87062-027-4\n | url=https://archive.org/details/handcartstozion00lero\n }}\n*{{cite book\n | last=Kimball\n | first=Stanley B.\n | authorlink=Stanley B. Kimball\n | title=Discovering Mormon Trails\n | year=1979\n | publisher=[[Deseret Book Company]]\n | oclc=5614526\n}}\n* {{cite book\n |last      = Lyman\n |first     = Paul D.\n |title     = The Willie Handcart Company: Their Day-by-Day Experiences, Including Trail Maps and Driving Directions\n |year      = 2006\n |publisher = [[BYU Studies Books]]\n |url       = https://byustudies.byu.edu/showTitle.aspx?title=201\n|archive-url = https://archive.today/20130626175152/https://byustudies.byu.edu/showTitle.aspx?title=201\n|url-status  = dead\n|archive-date = 2013-06-26\n}}\n* {{cite book\n | last=O'Dea\n | first=Thomas F.\n | title=The Mormons\n | url=https://archive.org/details/mormons0000odea\n | url-access=registration\n | year=1957\n | publisher=[[University of Chicago Press]]\n | location=Chicago\n | isbn= 0-226-61743-2\n}}\n* {{cite book\n | last=Olsen\n | first=Andrew D.\n | title=The Price We Paid: The Extraordinary Story of the Willie and Martin Handcart Pioneers\n | year=2006\n | publisher=[[Deseret Book Company]]\n | isbn=1-59038-624-8\n}}\n* {{cite journa