xchange Server]]\n| {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{Yes}} || {{No}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | [[Skype for Business Server]]\n| {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{No}} || {{No}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | [[Yammer|Yammer Enterprise]]\n| {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{No}} || {{No}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | Public website\n| {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{No}} || {{No}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | File storage and sharing\n| {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{No}} || {{Yes}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" |[[SharePoint]]\n| {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{No}} || {{Yes}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | [[Active Directory]] integration\n| {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{Yes}} || {{No}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | Site mailboxes\n| {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{No}} || {{No}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | [[Microsoft Office Mobile|Office mobile apps]]\n| {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{No}} || {{Yes}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | Advanced email {{clarify|reason=Clarification needed for information rights management, archiving and legal hold capabilities and unlimited storage.|text=|date=October 2014}}|| {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{No}} || {{No}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | Email storage per user\n|15 GB\n|50 GB\n|50 GB\n|50 GB\n|50 GB\n|none\n|50 GB\n|100 GB\n|Unknown\n|100 GB\n|50 GB\n|50 GB\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | eDiscovery Center\n| {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{No}} || {{No}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | Self-Service-Business Intelligence\n| {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{No}} || {{No}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | Voicemail\n| {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{No}} || {{Yes}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{No}}|| {{No}} \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | Custom Domain\n| {{Unknown}} || {{Yes}} || {{Unknown}} || {{Unknown}} || {{Unknown}} || {{Unknown}} || {{Yes}} ||{{Yes}} || {{Unknown}} ||{{Yes}}|| {{Yes}}|| {{No}} \n|-\n| colspan=\"13\" style=\"text-align: center;\" | {{Notelist|notes={{efn|name=winclint|Windows only}} }}\n|}\n\n==Reception==\n[[TechRadar]] gave the 2013 update of Office 365 a 4.5 out of 5, praising its administration interfaces for being accessible to users with any level of expertise, the seamless integration of SkyDrive Pro into the Office 2013 desktop applications, and the service as a whole for being suitable in small business environments, while still offering \"powerful\" options for use in larger companies (such as [[Data loss prevention software|data loss protection]] and the ability to integrate with a local [[Active Directory]] instance). However, the service was severely criticized for how it handled its 2013 update for existing users, and its lack of integration with services such as [[Skype]] and [[Yammer]].<ref name=techradar-365review/>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n==Further reading==\n{{refbegin|colwidth=30em}}\n* {{cite web\n  |url = https://www.microsoft.com/Presspass/press/2010/oct10/10-19Office365.mspx\n  |title = Microsoft Announces Office 365\n  |work = Microsoft News Center\n  |pu